      <title>兴奋剂使用者陷入致命的“第四波”阿片类药物流行</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/07/09/nx-s1-5015243/stimulant-users-meth-cocaine-coke-in-overdose-fourth-wave-opioid-epidemic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[每天仍有数百名美国人因吸毒过量而死亡。如今，越来越多的死亡与可卡因和冰毒等混合芬太尼的兴奋剂有关。有色人种男性受到的打击尤其严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/sections/shots-health-news/2024/07/09/nx-s1-5015243/stimulant-users-meth-cocaine-coke-in-overdose-fourth-wave-opioid-epidemic</guid>
